      "writtenOn": "2018-04-12T20:35:18Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "this isn\u0027t a dimension, though.\n\nFWIU Dimensions type defines a criteria of machines. Maybe rename it to MachineCriteria, MachinePoolDefinition or something.\n\nBTW, don\u0027t we use term \"bot\", not \"machine\"? V8 runs multiple bots on same machine, so I think s/machine/bot/ in this CL would be more accurate.",
