      "side": 1,
      "message": "I don\u0027t think strpair.Map serializes cleanly into a datastore entity since it\u0027s a list nested in a map, but otherwise this sgtm.\n\nI\u0027ll make PoolDescriptor :\u003d Dimensions + Host",
